Clone the following repository.
Switch to the repo: cd VFiT-Codebase
Make a virtual environment: python3 -m venv venv
Activate venv: (mac) source venv/bin/activate (windows) cd venv/Scripts/activate.bat (or activate.ps1 for powershell)
Install requirements: pip install -r r.txt
Activate backend server: cd backend && python3 manage.py runserver
Activate frontend server (new terminal): a. cd frontend b. npm install c. npm start
cd backend , mkdir media/savedModels